<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4753929>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 126–142: Lathrobium volutum spec. nov. (126–134) and L. trabale spec. nov. (135–142): habitus (126, 135); forebody (127, 136); male sternite VII (128, 138); male sternite VIII (129, 139); aedeagus in lateral view (130, 140); aedeagus in ventral view (131); apical portion of dorsal plate of aedeagus in lateral view (132); female sternite VIII (133, 141); female tergites IX–X (134, 142); abdominal segments III–VII (137). Scale bars: 126–127, 135–137: 1.0 mm; 128–131, 133–134, 138–142: 0.5 mm; 132: 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4753929/files/figure.png" .

